@baseUrl = http://localhost:18080/api
@clusterId = f8bb4d38-a02a-4d40-aa16-7d91a2673f5d-

### 1. Ping Test
GET {{baseUrl}}/ping

### 2. List All Clusters
GET {{baseUrl}}/clusters

### 3. Create a New Cluster
# @name createCluster
POST {{baseUrl}}/clusters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Local ES Cluster",
  "hosts": ["http://localhost:9200"],
  "color": "#18a058",
  "notes": "Testing via .http file"
}

### 4. Get Single Cluster
GET {{baseUrl}}/clusters/{{clusterId}}

### 5. Delete Cluster
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/clusters/{{clusterId}}

### 6. Proxy Request (Example: Get Cluster Info)
GET {{baseUrl}}/proxy/_cluster/health
X-Cluster-ID: {{clusterId}}